{"tid":1438482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打經濟牌係政府計劃既phrase 2","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:21:11.000Z","uid":18679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e44d8a85a6f9d7b24264e52bc22ac52b8761255b","tid":1438482,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:52:14.000Z","msg":"從來香港最重要既係經濟 <br />\n基本上8成香港人睇重經濟多於政治理念<br />\n反送中一開始咁多人支持就係因為<br />\n送中會威脅到香港獨特既營商環境<br />\n外資唔敢黎 香港食得屎<br />\n<br />\n但一路落黎抗爭既議題已經由反送中發展成 獨立調查委員會 / 林鄭下台 / 徹回暴動定性等<br />\n<br />\n而政府一路等緊既就係示威對經濟既影響<br />\n所以呢段期間一路縮 一路等 一路等示威者力量慢慢減弱<br />\n呢個就係佔中既劇本<br />\n其間仲用埋郡眾鬥郡眾呢條中共舊橋<br />\n當然執行上政府柒到一個點 大家有眼睇<br />\n結果示威者既力量黎到8月不單無明顯減弱<br />\n仲因為大量同popo對戰而經驗值升左幾級<br />\n而且今次唔同佔中 每次抗爭完都可以返屋企休息<br />\n而popo既暴行都直接影響到各區街坊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">黎緊政府唔會好似7月咁 警黑鬥郡眾<br />\n8月主題將會係 經濟鬥郡眾</span></strong></ins></span><br />\n大家都知其實示威影響得經濟幾多<br />\n買gear 飯券都買到窮 <br />\n真正主因係貿易戰<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: purple;\">但政府會將呢d spin落去示威者到<br />\n令到中立 淺黃 商家佬唔再鬧黑警<br />\n轉而鬧示威者</span></ins></strong><br />\n所以8月抗爭一定要轉tone<br />\n文宣大大加強<br />\n民間記者會個焦點轉返落政府到<br />\n多d去機場抗爭<br />\n國際戰線多d上外國媒體<br />\n<br />\n總之8月抗爭 popo繼續屌 但個焦點一定要去返政府頭目 同埋文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論但不分化不指罵"},{"pid":"363755a321679614a0ad01e12f629b6061a9e460","tid":1438482,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:53:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f536ce94adb54077341bce6ea5b9349b5e09b86","tid":1438482,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"500ee47e0d8799fec877bee78625a57411e572be","tid":1438482,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:00:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span><br />\n[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=8kP02BZom8b0sC5RUQuyVStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=61e2b9e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有31,705/100,000個簽名（10 Aug 2019 at 02:47）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n香港警察 恐怖組織<br />\n過期化武 無差別襲擊<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1bc58aecd88b89f9748eee0e0b81f836ba7dbd64","tid":1438482,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:00:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家覺得加返deadline升級好唔好？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n依家情況同上一個月差多<br />\n又係做好多嘢令到<span style=\"color: red;\">行動失去咗個目的</span>同埋冇時限搞到好似好迷失方向，和理非定勇武定包圍，行動上都係冇共識<br />\n加返deadline有好處<br />\n1.重申五大訴求，目標清晰，行動出師有名<br />\n2.訂立短中期行動計劃，例：今個禮拜和理非回合，唔回應就下個禮拜升級勇武行動<br />\n3.有計劃容易整合文宣<br />\n4.自己人有清晰目標，喺啲狗每日shift focus之下叫人專注返都易啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得 和理非&gt;deadline&gt;勇武升級 嘅抗爭概念<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1431556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1431556</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"acc7ea5cecbcc789adee882ce1f7e7b98b046a89","tid":1438482,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b7639d6bd56c7b34ed6e451ba9c9361ffb287c","tid":1438482,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:07:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span>"},{"pid":"e607d4203c567ff498168d0ff3d3dbfa6caa63c2","tid":1438482,"uid":94441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X4ZJvS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX4ZJvS4.jpg&h=d588c027&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29dede26c407a1bcd507c9475e951adb3b0d6ced","tid":1438482,"uid":18679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9d6702fe828aa87ee74321ba9c131a6251b